INFO.name: QUERY_STRING
INFO.value: SELECT ID_AR,DATE_FORMAT(DATE_OBS,"%Y-%m-%dT%T") as DATE_OBS,NOAA_NUMBER,FEAT_HG_LAT_DEG,FEAT_AREA_DEG2,FEAT_X_ARCSEC,FEAT_Y_ARCSEC,FEAT_MAX_INT,FEAT_MIN_INT,FEAT_MEAN_INT FROM VIEW_AR_GUI WHERE (DATE_OBS BETWEEN "2003-04-01T00:00" AND "2003-04-16T00:00") AND (ID_OBSERVATORY IN (1)) ORDER BY DATE_OBS ASC

FIELD.name: FEAT_HG_LAT_DEG
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Heliographic latitude of the SS gravity centre in degrees

FIELD.name: FEAT_AREA_DEG2
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Area of the SS in square degrees

FIELD.name: FEAT_X_ARCSEC
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: X Heliocentric coordinates of the SS gravity centre in arcsec

FIELD.name: FEAT_Y_ARCSEC
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Y Heliocentric coordinates of the SS gravity centre in arcsec

FIELD.name: FEAT_MAX_INT
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Type 3 max. intensity value, in units of the original observation

FIELD.name: FEAT_MIN_INT
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: SS min. intensity value, in units of the original observation

FIELD.name: FEAT_MEAN_INT
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Type 3 mean intensity value, in units of the original observation
